category.catDesc:
Imprecise date value(s) augmented with @notBefore and @notAfter
                            inferred based on date rules (e.g. yyyy has @notBefore="yyyy-01-01" and
                            @notAfter="yyyy-12-31"; yyyy-mm has @notBefore="yyyy-mm-01" and
                            @notAfter="yyyy-mm-dd" where dd is either 28, 29, 30, or 31 based on
                            month and year)

[Contemporary Volumes] Imprecise date value(s) augmented with
                            @notBefore and @notAfter inferred during consultation with
                            editor(s)/compiler(s)
